entries.title_d: Strike Back: Destroy the Kimogila supplier of the infested cargo.
entries.title: Lok System: Destroy the Kimogila Battlelord
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 Station Command: < \#pcontrast1 Well done. Return to Dathomir Space whenever you're ready. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_target_d: Sent cargo that was infested with lice.
entries.quest_location_d: An area in the Lok System
entries.quest_escort_d: Secondary objectives: destroy at all costs. Leave no witnesses.
entries.failed_escape: \#pcontrast3 Station Command: < \#pcontrast1 The Kimogila battlelord has escaped! This is unacceptable. Report back to the station for another attempt. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_wiped_out: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 All escort craft have been destroyed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 An escort craft has been destroyed, %DI remain \#pcontrast3 >
entries.destroy_escort: \#pcontrast3 Station Command: < \#pcontrast1 Great job, now finish off his escort. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.assassinate_success: \#pcontrast3 Station Command: < \#pcontrast1 The Kimogila battlelord has been destroyed!  That will teach them to mess with us. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_2: \#pcontrast3 Station Command: \#pcontrast1 The Kimogila battlelord's craft has dropped from hyperspace.  Transmitting his location now. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_1: \#pcontrast3 Station Command: < \#pcontrast1 The Kimogila battlelord will be in the range shorly, stand by for coordinates. \#pcontrast3 >
